{"tid":1952821,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(新聞分享) Mail Online: 支那武肺大龍鳳 The Great Cover-up","createTime":"2020-03-31T23:42:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T02:43:24.000Z","uid":14918,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6b252abb40aca8236937e6d33deadb851c285163","tid":1952821,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T23:42:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />首先呢篇news好新鮮滾熱辣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />內容梗係屌柒支那隱瞞疫情，導致世界大流行<br />\n<br />\n篇文分左六小段，每段都係講支那點隱瞞，造假數，搶外國資源扮好心統戰人<br />\n<br />\n1. Initial outbreak<br />\n2. Early reports<br />\n3. Origin of the virus<br />\n4. Infection total<br />\n5. Death total <br />\n6. Chinese aid packages<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8172369/China-tried-cover-coronavirus-not-telling-truth.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-8172369%2FChina-tried-cover-coronavirus-not-telling-truth.html&d=J1zZABjvT6n5gtW5jiJIholeFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=99af6e49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8172369/China-tried-cover-coronavirus-not-telling-truth.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最感動就係見到歐洲人留comment <br />\n佢地意識到要強硬對付支那<br />\n要禁施禁運<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要求支那賠償<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EqELeAz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEqELeAz.png&h=3d7e9ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FxgE3u0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFxgE3u0.png&h=3647739e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93c27793cb4a23b74ec0aa9adbbddc1c47cbe815","tid":1952821,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T00:08:57.000Z","msg